{"tid":845562,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"[求救]大埔見到隻流浪狗","createTime":"2018-10-02T18:34:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-03T07:02:49.000Z","uid":87397,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"5515e5a8ea36cf62de3a7167304f330c272c1ac9","tid":845562,"uid":87397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T18:34:45.000Z","msg":"我地係大埔某屋苑見到隻流浪狗<br />\n看更趕極佢都唔走<br />\n其實佢似走失多過流浪 好乾淨<br />\n同埋第一次係呢頭出現<br />\n有位ching由11點看住佢<br />\n到宜加2點半 隻狗仲係度<br />\n我地買左啲罐頭+水佢飲<br />\n一下就食哂<br />\ncall左義工機構諗住check晶片<br />\n但太夜無人覆<br />\n在場我地三個人全部未養過狗<br />\n其實都有少少驚狗<br />\n有無巴絲可以幫下手？<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/pz90r5is\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fpz90r5is&h=2e182df2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d56a93bb928810d7680bcddde8ed19946ece9e01","tid":845562,"uid":87397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T18:40:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cacb5d9236edea81c2a5e79c9e3da98a8f876142","tid":845562,"uid":64913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T18:42:12.000Z","msg":"大埔邊頭？如果有人養，應該有狗帶。附近有HKDR既場，唔知會唔會係果度既狗<br />\n<br />\n唔洗驚，你可以握個拳頭，慢慢接近佢比佢聞下"},{"pid":"d93a433ba0ef6d92627cd7c4831b90e7c74cdb4e","tid":845562,"uid":87397,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T18:42:27.000Z","msg":"佢真係好乖<br />\n唔吠 就咁訓係度<br />\n問過哂朋友 無人可以收留佢一晚？<br />\n我地又唔識捉佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cab5683f47dd79215380a6cb40a9beca0310e138","tid":845562,"uid":28624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T18:43:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ab4eb3a6c1ca1def32c2b431f3f8b2d6a56ad3d","tid":845562,"uid":99568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T18:44:27.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9267d8faddd44b3c1b01202fd01ec13d482836a8","tid":845562,"uid":87397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cacb5d9236ed